to Huanshang Village to negotiate.

123
00:09:11,530 --> 00:09:13,390
He came back with six conditions.

124
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:15,750
What are those six conditions?

125
00:09:15,810 --> 00:09:17,210
Better if you don't know.

126
00:09:17,530 --> 00:09:18,260
Each one

127
00:09:19,530 --> 00:09:20,930
could cost you your life.

128
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:24,650
