won't get him anywhere.

156
00:10:35,290 --> 00:10:37,020
You're stuck with a master like that.

157
00:10:37,020 --> 00:10:37,930
Who knows what'll happen

158
00:10:37,930 --> 00:10:39,020
from here on out?

159
00:10:40,570 --> 00:10:41,770
He's a lost cause.

160
00:10:43,140 --> 00:10:44,140
No wonder Yuan Shikai

161
00:10:44,140 --> 00:10:45,260
is so aggressive.

162
00:10:46,140 --> 00:10:47,570
He has seen through it all.

163
00:10:47,570 --> 00:10:49,300
He's dead set on seizing power.

164
00:10:53,530 --> 00:10:54,290
As for you,

165
00:10:54,770 --> 00:10:55,410
my son,

166
00:10:57,260 --> 00:10:59,900
I'm afraid you'll end up
like a hunchback falling over,

167
00:10:59,900 --> 00:11:01,410
losing out on both sides.

168
00:11:03,900 --> 00:11:05,960
Things aren't looking good already.

169
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,310
Zhang Shaozeng, Lan Tianwei, and others

170
00:11:08,310 --> 00:11:11,170
have committed a grave offense
by petitioning the military in Luanzhou.

171
00:11:11,170 --> 00:11:11,930
These two just so happen to be

172
00:11:11,930 --> 00:11:13,930
my classmates from
our time studying in Japan.

173
00:11:13,930 --> 00:11:15,900
So that gave them a handle to grab onto,

174
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:18,430
claiming my personnel policies were flawed.

175
00:11:19,260 --> 00:11:21,320
The Prince Regent has just suggested

176
00:11:21,380 --> 00:11:22,640
that, as a precaution,

177
00:11:22,770 --> 00:11:25,370
Kaizhi's military power
should be taken away.

178
00:11:27,650 --> 00:11:28,260
I really don't know

179
00:11:28,260 --> 00:11:29,720
how to handle this matter.

180
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:32,580
If I'm a bit too harsh,

181
00:11:33,930 --> 00:11:35,790
it might push him into rebellion.

182
00:11:43,650 --> 00:11:44,410
Son,

183
00:11:45,450 --> 00:11:47,380
leaves fall when their time comes.

184
00:11:48,530 --> 00:11:49,410
No matter

185
00:11:50,380 --> 00:11:51,910
if the rooster crows or not,

186
00:11:52,450 --> 00:11:53,170
the sun

187
00:11:53,770 --> 00:11:55,300
will still rise in the east.

