200
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:35,380
Reserve them for our troops' use.

201
00:12:35,380 --> 00:12:36,020
Yes, sir.

202
00:12:36,140 --> 00:12:36,940
Wait a moment.

203
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:39,650
Kaizhi,

204
00:12:40,930 --> 00:12:41,900
intercepting the court's supplies

