intended for suppressing
the Wuchang rebellion,

206
00:12:42,950 --> 00:12:43,750
I'm afraid...

207
00:12:45,650 --> 00:12:46,290
Hold it.

208
00:12:46,770 --> 00:12:47,650
That's what we'll do.

209
00:12:47,650 --> 00:12:48,380
Yes, sir.

210
00:12:58,390 --> 00:12:59,810
Report: There's a telegram
from General Liang Xiang

211
00:12:59,810 --> 00:13:02,210
of the Beijing Military Advisory Council.

212
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:02,900
Read it.

213
00:13:03,020 --> 00:13:03,550
Yes, sir.

214
00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:04,930
Yuan Shikai has officially

215
00:13:04,930 --> 00:13:06,140
accepted the court's appointment

216
00:13:06,140 --> 00:13:07,900
and has left Zhangde
to oversee the southern troops.

217
00:13:07,900 --> 00:13:08,570
He has now arrived

218
00:13:08,570 --> 00:13:10,260
at the Beiyang General Headquarters
in Xinyang.

219
00:13:10,260 --> 00:13:11,350
Our Beiyang Army

220
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,900
has launched a full-scale offensive
towards Hankou today.

221
00:13:12,900 --> 00:13:15,760
