the advance is going smoothly.

222
00:13:22,050 --> 00:13:24,290
Mr. Yuan really gets things done,
doesn't he?

223
00:13:24,290 --> 00:13:26,020
He's just made his appearance,

224
00:13:26,170 --> 00:13:28,500
and already it's a full house of applause.

225
00:13:29,020 --> 00:13:32,750
So, when it comes to intercepting
military supplies headed south,

226
00:13:32,850 --> 00:13:34,810
I hope you'll proceed carefully.

227
00:13:38,650 --> 00:13:39,500
Carefully?

228
00:13:40,530 --> 00:13:41,730
How careful exactly?

229
00:13:42,930 --> 00:13:44,530
