245
00:14:39,900 --> 00:14:41,430
He's just putting on a show.

246
00:14:41,650 --> 00:14:42,410
Good cop, bad cop,

247
00:14:42,410 --> 00:14:44,270
he's playing both roles himself.

248
00:14:44,530 --> 00:14:46,900
