250
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:51,930
He used the excuse of resting
in Huanshang Village

251
00:14:51,930 --> 00:14:52,570
to set the stage

252
00:14:52,570 --> 00:14:53,650
for everything.

253
00:14:53,930 --> 00:14:56,020
