to suppress the revolution,

254
00:14:56,020 --> 00:14:57,050
while secretly nurturing
revolutionary forces,

255
00:14:57,050 --> 00:15:00,510
letting them grow strong enough
to threaten the court itself.

256
00:15:01,930 --> 00:15:04,460
