258
00:15:07,770 --> 00:15:08,830
With this victory,

259
00:15:09,140 --> 00:15:11,340
won't he become even harder to control?

260
00:15:27,260 --> 00:15:28,660
This is Zaitao speaking.

261
00:15:28,770 --> 00:15:29,300
Go ahead.

262
00:15:31,050 --> 00:15:31,450
What?

263
00:15:33,140 --> 00:15:34,450
Li Renjun of the Twelfth Brigade,

264
00:15:34,450 --> 00:15:36,510
