00:16:28,650 --> 00:16:29,260
But have you considered

281
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:30,530
another scenario?

282
00:16:31,170 --> 00:16:32,670
If Yuan resolves the chaos in Wuhan

283
00:16:32,670 --> 00:16:33,800
within a few days

284
00:16:34,540 --> 00:16:35,720
and rides the wave of his victory

285
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:37,140
to suddenly return to Beijing,

286
00:16:37,140 --> 00:16:38,140
will we still have

287
00:16:39,380 --> 00:16:41,140
any leverage to hold him back?

288
00:16:50,020 --> 00:16:51,530
Well, I think we should go ahead with this.

289
00:16:51,530 --> 00:16:52,930
Let's play chess as well.

290
00:16:53,380 --> 00:16:54,260
How should we play?

291
00:16:54,260 --> 00:16:54,930
Luanzhou.

292
00:16:55,900 --> 00:16:58,020
The trouble with Zhang and Lan
in Luanzhou isn't settled yet.

293
00:16:58,020 --> 00:16:58,800
Why not

294
00:16:59,290 --> 00:16:59,980
send Yang Kaizhi there

295
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:01,170
to calm things down?

296
00:17:01,930 --> 00:17:02,460
That way,

297
00:17:03,140 --> 00:17:04,819
we stabilize Luanzhou,

298
00:17:05,210 --> 00:17:06,380
and also transfer Yang Kaizhi

299
00:17:06,380 --> 00:17:08,010
and the Sixth Division troops away,

300
00:17:08,010 --> 00:17:09,210
to avoid any mishaps.

301
00:17:11,140 --> 00:17:12,450
You're also capable of such trickery.

302
00:17:12,450 --> 00:17:13,339
I'm not stupid!

303
00:17:15,930 --> 00:17:17,589
Draft the order immediately.

304
00:17:18,410 --> 00:17:18,970
Alright.

305
00:17:38,580 --> 00:17:39,210
Hello?

306
00:17:41,410 --> 00:17:42,930
It's me, Zaitao.

307
00:17:46,190 --> 00:17:47,120
I'm listening.

308
00:17:57,410 --> 00:17:58,930
I have nothing to say.

309
00:17:59,620 --> 00:18:00,880
Since you've decided.

310
00:18:07,140 --> 00:18:10,270
Who should I hand over
the Military Advisory Council to?

311
00:18:13,170 --> 00:18:13,860
Alright.

312
00:18:16,650 --> 00:18:18,450
What about the Imperial Guards?

313
00:18:21,450 --> 00:18:22,380
That's fine too.

314
00:18:24,650 --> 00:18:25,820
I'll do as you say.

315
00:18:26,690 --> 00:18:27,650
That's it then.

316
00:18:47,380 --> 00:18:48,340
What's going on?

317
00:18:50,970 --> 00:18:53,430
Zaifeng has already dissolved the cabinet.

318
00:18:54,210 --> 00:18:55,690
Dissolved the cabinet?

319
00:18:56,930 --> 00:18:58,100
He also dismissed Zaixun

320
00:18:58,100 --> 00:19:00,140
from his post as Minister of the Navy.

321
00:19:00,140 --> 00:19:00,930
What?

322
00:19:02,210 --> 00:19:03,820
My position as
Chairman of the Military Advisory Council

323
00:19:03,820 --> 00:19:05,080
has also been revoked.

324
00:19:07,140 --> 00:19:08,580
For now, I'll temporarily take over

325
00:19:08,580 --> 00:19:09,470
as the Minister in charge of

326
00:19:09,470 --> 00:19:11,130
training the Imperial Guards

327
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:12,620
until

328
00:19:15,620 --> 00:19:19,280
the new Prime Minister arrives
in the capital and assumes office.

329
00:19:21,860 --> 00:19:23,650
Who is the new Prime Minister?

330
00:19:25,450 --> 00:19:26,580
Who else could it be?

331
00:19:28,410 --> 00:19:29,210
Yuan Shikai.

332
00:19:47,580 --> 00:19:49,100
I knew this day would come.

333
00:19:51,690 --> 00:19:52,950
I just didn't expect it

334
00:19:55,510 --> 00:19:56,560
to come so soon.

335
00:20:11,690 --> 00:20:12,620
Tufang,

336
00:20:14,450 --> 00:20:15,860
take whatever you want

337
00:20:16,230 --> 00:20:17,820
from here.

338
00:20:19,410 --> 00:20:21,210
It's not mine anymore anyway.

339
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:06,690
Hello?

340
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:11,240
There's

341
00:21:12,820 --> 00:21:13,930
no longer

342
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:17,320
a Chairman of
the Military Advisory Council here.

343
00:21:36,650 --> 00:21:44,120
[On November 1, 1911, the Qing government announced the dismissal of the royally
dominated cabinet and appointed Yuan Shikai as Prime Minister of the Imperial Cabinet.]

344
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:47,170
Is this what they call
suppressing a rebellion?

345
00:21:47,170 --> 00:21:48,340
This is a massacre.

346
00:21:48,690 --> 00:21:49,860
Feng Guozhang is rampaging

347
00:21:49,860 --> 00:21:50,950
through Hankou, burning and looting.

348
00:21:50,950 --> 00:21:52,100
Blood runs like rivers.

349
00:21:52,100 --> 00:21:54,030
How could any human do such a thing?

350
00:21:58,930 --> 00:21:59,690
Maichen,

351
00:22:00,100 --> 00:22:01,820
send a telegram to Beijing in my name.

352
00:22:01,820 --> 00:22:02,930
I want him impeached for the crime

353
00:22:02,930 --> 00:22:04,100
of slaughtering civilians.

354
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:05,660
Kaizhi, calm down.

355
00:22:05,770 --> 00:22:07,240
No! This is a matter of principle.

356
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:08,240
We have to send it.

357
00:22:09,100 --> 00:22:10,450
Don't be so scholarly about it.

358
00:22:10,450 --> 00:22:11,620
What's wrong with being scholarly?

359
00:22:11,620 --> 00:22:13,100
I am a scholar, damn it!

360
00:22:13,340 --> 00:22:14,100
Send it!

361
00:22:27,010 --> 00:22:27,810
Commander Li,

362
00:22:28,340 --> 00:22:30,070
you must help us settle scores!

363
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:31,690
That dude, Yang,

364
00:22:31,930 --> 00:22:32,690
is dragging us

365
00:22:32,690 --> 00:22:33,690
into a mess!

366
00:22:34,100 --> 00:22:35,010
That's right.

367
00:22:35,460 --> 00:22:36,820
Mr. Yuan has come back to power.

368
00:22:36,820 --> 00:22:38,380
We have nothing to fear now.

369
00:22:39,340 --> 00:22:40,210
I think

370
00:22:40,450 --> 00:22:41,930
we should just tie him up.

371
00:22:46,690 --> 00:22:47,620
Qianli,

372
00:22:48,170 --> 00:22:49,170
you give an order.

373
00:22:49,500 --> 00:22:50,820
We, the veterans of the Beiyang

374
00:22:50,820 --> 00:22:52,130
Wuwei Corps Right Division,

375
00:22:52,130 --> 00:22:53,590
will all follow your lead.

376
00:22:53,690 --> 00:22:54,580
Yes, that's right.

377
00:22:54,580 --> 00:22:55,910
Please make a decision.

378
00:23:04,930 --> 00:23:07,010
I know what happened.

379
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:10,830
Let's take our time
to think of a better solution.

380
00:23:11,650 --> 00:23:13,170
Can't do it by force.

381
00:23:16,210 --> 00:23:17,930
After all, we're brothers-in-arms.

382
00:23:17,930 --> 00:23:18,410
You...

383
00:23:18,450 --> 00:23:19,860
How can you call someone like that

384
00:23:19,860 --> 00:23:20,860
your brother?

385
00:23:20,930 --> 00:23:21,580
Yeah,

386
00:23:21,650 --> 00:23:22,410
Commander Li,

387
00:23:22,410 --> 00:23:23,860
we can't let Yang Kaizhi

388
00:23:24,010 --> 00:23:25,340
get us into big trouble!

389
00:23:25,410 --> 00:23:26,930
Yes, please do something.

390
00:23:27,100 --> 00:23:28,360
Commander Li, please make up your mind.

391
00:23:28,360 --> 00:23:29,220
That's enough!

392
00:23:30,930 --> 00:23:31,590
Get the hell

393
00:23:31,860 --> 00:23:33,390
back to your units and wait!

394
00:23:38,170 --> 00:23:39,170
Let's go.

395
00:23:48,350 --> 00:23:49,110
Sir!

396
00:23:52,170 --> 00:23:52,750
Commander Li,

397
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:53,730
the Ministry of War sent a telegram

398
00:23:53,730 --> 00:23:54,450
to our Twelfth Brigade,

399
00:23:54,450 --> 00:23:56,450
specifically requesting your receipt.

400
00:23:56,450 --> 00:23:57,860
The Ministry of War
sent it directly to me?

401
00:23:57,860 --> 00:23:58,450
Yes, sir.

402
00:23:58,930 --> 00:23:59,730
Read it for me.

403
00:24:00,210 --> 00:24:01,170
The Ministry of War orders

404
00:24:01,170 --> 00:24:02,820
General Commander Yang Kaizhi
of the Sixth Division

405
00:24:02,820 --> 00:24:04,580
to depart for Luanzhou
upon receiving this telegram

406
00:24:04,580 --> 00:24:06,680
to pacify the troops led by Zhang Shaozeng

407
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:07,890
and Lan Tianwei.

408
00:24:08,100 --> 00:24:09,910
No excuses for refusal will be accepted.

409
00:24:09,910 --> 00:24:10,690
Command of the Sixth Division

410
00:24:10,690 --> 00:24:12,410
will be temporarily assumed
by Brigade Commander Li Renjun.

411
00:24:12,410 --> 00:24:14,540
This order is from the Ministry of War.

412
00:24:27,770 --> 00:24:39,190
[The Sixth Division of Beiyang Army]

413
00:24:49,580 --> 00:24:50,340
Buzhou,

414
00:24:50,620 --> 00:24:52,010
the General Commander's safety

415
00:24:52,010 --> 00:24:53,380
in Luanzhou all counts on you guys.

416
00:24:53,380 --> 00:24:55,380
Yes, please rest assured,
Brigade Commander.

417
00:24:55,380 --> 00:24:55,930
I, Ma Buzhou,

418
00:24:55,930 --> 00:24:56,690
will protect

419
00:24:56,690 --> 00:24:58,290
Commander Yang with my life.

420
00:24:58,930 --> 00:25:00,190
It's not that serious.

421
00:25:00,650 --> 00:25:01,450
Zhang and Lan

422
00:25:01,450 --> 00:25:02,710
are just making a show.

423
00:25:03,170 --> 00:25:04,580
If they really rebelled, why

424
00:25:04,580 --> 00:25:06,410
would they bother
sending political statements?

425
00:25:06,410 --> 00:25:09,210
They'd have already
marched straight to Beijing!

426
00:25:11,930 --> 00:25:13,530
If I'm worried about anyone,

427
00:25:14,350 --> 00:25:16,240
it should be you, Qianli.

428
00:25:17,390 --> 00:25:18,630
Now that your Mr. Yuan

429
00:25:18,650 --> 00:25:20,250
is at the height of his power,

430
00:25:21,170 --> 00:25:22,450
you must be both

431
00:25:22,620 --> 00:25:24,620
surprised and exhilarated, right?

432
00:25:26,170 --> 00:25:27,490
The ten-year bet

433
00:25:28,410 --> 00:25:29,670
is about to be settled.

434
00:25:33,170 --> 00:25:35,170
Don't say that, General Commander.

435
00:25:37,030 --> 00:25:38,310
Honestly,

436
00:25:39,930 --> 00:25:41,100
can I, Yang Kaizhi,

437
00:25:41,820 --> 00:25:43,860
still command you, Li Renjun?

438
00:25:48,100 --> 00:25:48,930
Kaizhi,

439
00:25:49,930 --> 00:25:50,970
the court has retained your post

440
00:25:50,970 --> 00:25:52,990
as General Commander
of the Sixth Division.

441
00:25:52,990 --> 00:25:54,380
I, Li Renjun, see you as my big bro

442
00:25:54,380 --> 00:25:56,240
both officially and personally.

443
00:25:57,100 --> 00:25:58,340
If not,

444
00:25:59,170 --> 00:26:00,620
I will be a jerk.

445
00:26:01,820 --> 00:26:02,380
Maichen,

446
00:26:03,170 --> 00:26:04,170
did you hear that?

447
00:26:05,010 --> 00:26:07,310
Qianli talked in such an affirmative tone.

448
00:26:07,310 --> 00:26:08,750
Be a witness for me.

449
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:09,410
Okay.

450
00:26:15,930 --> 00:26:16,860
Don't worry.

451
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:19,610
The friendship
between us three is unbreakable.

452
00:26:19,930 --> 00:26:22,340
"If life could remain
the way it was when we first met."

453
00:26:22,340 --> 00:26:22,920
Renjun,

454
00:26:24,010 --> 00:26:25,540
how beautiful this line is.

455
00:26:27,060 --> 00:26:27,750
Giddy up!

456
00:26:46,860 --> 00:26:47,930
News! Newspaper!

457
00:26:48,210 --> 00:26:49,820
The battle in Wuchang is deadlocked

458
00:26:49,820 --> 00:26:51,340
with all countries firmly staying neutral!

459
00:26:51,340 --> 00:26:52,870
Come on, I want a newspaper.

460
00:26:52,930 --> 00:26:53,820
Got it!

461
00:26:54,620 --> 00:26:56,250
Naval warships stationed in Shanghai

462
00:26:56,250 --> 00:26:58,340
have all rushed to Hankou
for reinforcements!

463
00:26:58,340 --> 00:26:59,580
Extra! Extra!

464
00:27:02,430 --> 00:27:07,520
[Shanghai's Ningbo Chamber of Commerce]

465
00:27:08,650 --> 00:27:09,580
You've arrived.

466
00:27:09,930 --> 00:27:10,930
Thank you.

467
00:27:47,100 --> 00:27:48,510
Don't worry, manager.

468
00:27:48,790 --> 00:27:49,930
As long as all the ingredients are ready,
it's fine.

469
00:27:49,930 --> 00:27:52,190
Three tables for lunch, four for dinner.

470
00:27:52,210 --> 00:27:53,450
No problem on my end.

471
00:27:56,080 --> 00:27:56,810
Shuhong.

472
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:58,160
Come with me.

473
00:28:08,690 --> 00:28:10,580
Have all the invitations been delivered?

474
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:11,440
All delivered.

475
00:28:11,580 --> 00:28:12,490
The commander of Wusong Fort

476
00:28:12,490 --> 00:28:13,450
can't make it for lunch,

477
00:28:13,450 --> 00:28:15,250
but he promised to come tonight.

478
00:28:15,860 --> 00:28:17,060
Battalion Commander Lai Xi
of the Patrol and Defense Battalion

479
00:28:17,060 --> 00:28:18,100
declined the invitation.

480
00:28:18,100 --> 00:28:19,560
He's close to Liang Xiang.

481
00:28:19,580 --> 00:28:20,860
So he wanted to keep his distance.

482
00:28:20,860 --> 00:28:21,920
He was ignoring us.

483
00:28:22,340 --> 00:28:24,400
Because of that radio deal last time.

484
00:28:24,930 --> 00:28:25,820
Perhaps.

485
00:28:26,410 --> 00:28:27,340
But his adjutant is willing

486
00:28:27,340 --> 00:28:29,070
to come and talk in the evening.

487
00:28:29,270 --> 00:28:30,200
That's good too.

488
00:28:31,580 --> 00:28:32,860
So, it seems

489
00:28:33,170 --> 00:28:35,690
all the military units
stationed in Shanghai,

490
00:28:35,690 --> 00:28:38,430
except for the Garrison Commander
of the Jiangnan General Manufacturing Bureau,

491
00:28:38,430 --> 00:28:40,060
are in touch with us now.

492
00:28:40,410 --> 00:28:41,930
It's the trend of the times.

493
00:28:41,930 --> 00:28:42,930
We call it dinner,

494
00:28:42,970 --> 00:28:43,820
but everyone

495
00:28:43,820 --> 00:28:44,990
knows what it's really about.

496
00:28:44,990 --> 00:28:46,100
No one says it out loud.

497
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:49,620
The wise adapt to circumstances.

498
00:28:50,410 --> 00:28:53,410
It's like a sheet of paper on a window.

499
00:28:54,170 --> 00:28:56,170
Someone just has to poke through it.

500
00:28:56,170 --> 00:29:00,170
This way, Chen Yingshi, Song Chen
and the others in the merchant militia

501
00:29:00,210 --> 00:29:02,580
won't have to fear bullets anymore.

502
00:29:13,860 --> 00:29:15,180
The bullets you've received,

503
00:29:14,570 --> 00:29:18,300
[Shanghai Merchant Militia Station]

504
00:29:15,650 --> 00:29:16,650
if they don't need to be fired,

505
00:29:16,650 --> 00:29:18,110
it's best not to fire them.

506
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:20,040
A prosperous Shanghai

507
00:29:19,890 --> 00:29:23,740
[Chen Qimei from Revolutionary Party]

508
00:29:20,100 --> 00:29:21,760
must be won without fighting.

509
00:29:22,210 --> 00:29:25,210
This aligns with the hopes
of all sectors in Shanghai.

510
00:29:25,930 --> 00:29:26,860
So.

511
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:29,100
Song Chen.

512
00:29:30,210 --> 00:29:31,170
Your father

513
00:29:31,410 --> 00:29:33,010
has my respect.

514
00:29:34,170 --> 00:29:34,900
He's determined to

515
00:29:34,900 --> 00:29:37,100
take back Shanghai at the dinner table.

516
00:29:37,490 --> 00:29:38,730
It's a bold idea.

517
00:29:39,930 --> 00:29:40,850
However,

518
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:42,430
we

519
00:29:43,060 --> 00:29:44,520
must be prepared to bleed,

520
00:29:44,520 --> 00:29:45,780
prepared to sacrifice

521
00:29:46,100 --> 00:29:47,300
and prepared to fail.

522
00:29:48,410 --> 00:29:50,290
I, Chen Yingshi, have lived my life

523
00:29:50,290 --> 00:29:51,820
with history as my witness.

524
00:29:51,820 --> 00:29:52,930
Standing in this world,

525
00:29:52,930 --> 00:29:54,060
I am here for revolution.

526
00:29:54,060 --> 00:29:54,920
Even if we fail,

527
00:29:55,010 --> 00:29:56,870
I will start another revolution.

528
00:29:57,930 --> 00:29:59,170
I am prepared.

529
00:29:59,380 --> 00:30:00,240
What about you?

530
00:30:00,850 --> 00:30:02,060
Are you all prepared?

531
00:30:02,140 --> 00:30:05,070
Sacrifice for the revolution,
restore China!

532
00:30:05,100 --> 00:30:07,510
Sacrifice for the revolution,
restore China!

533
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:09,860
Sacrifice for the revolution,
restore China!

534
00:30:09,860 --> 00:30:12,340
Restore China! Restore China!

535
00:30:17,580 --> 00:30:18,620
Come, come.

536
00:30:29,180 --> 00:30:29,930
Chairman Song, Chairman Song.

537
00:30:29,930 --> 00:30:30,930
Here’s to you.

538
00:30:31,410 --> 00:30:33,410
Excuse me, nature calls.

539
00:30:33,620 --> 00:30:34,450
We'll talk when I get back.

540
00:30:34,450 --> 00:30:35,210
We’ll talk later.

541
00:30:35,210 --> 00:30:36,610
Alright, take your time.

542
00:30:42,860 --> 00:30:45,010
Shuhong, there's new information.

543
00:30:45,340 --> 00:30:46,490
The commander of Wusong Fort

544
00:30:46,490 --> 00:30:47,170
told me that

545
00:30:47,470 --> 00:30:48,820
the Nanjing Viceroy's Office

546
00:30:48,820 --> 00:30:49,620
has sent

547
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:50,970
a confidential order today

548
00:30:50,970 --> 00:30:52,170
to all military units in Shanghai.

549
00:30:52,170 --> 00:30:54,310
The merchant militia
has been labeled as rebels.

550
00:30:54,310 --> 00:30:56,440
Once caught, they'll all be executed.

551
00:30:57,210 --> 00:30:58,340
Go notify

552
00:30:58,340 --> 00:30:59,930
Li Xiehe and Chen Qimei right away.

553
00:30:59,930 --> 00:31:01,450
The operation must be moved up.

554
00:31:01,450 --> 00:31:02,180
Understood.

555
00:31:09,970 --> 00:31:12,570
[Jiangnan General Manufacturing Bureau]

556
00:31:39,140 --> 00:31:40,070
Save them!

557
00:31:59,010 --> 00:31:59,740
Instructor.

558
00:32:00,860 --> 00:32:01,910
We're out of bullets.

559
00:32:01,910 --> 00:32:02,910
What should we do?

560
00:32:30,460 --> 00:32:31,110
Father!

561
00:32:34,580 --> 00:32:35,690
How is Yingshi now?

562
00:32:36,130 --> 00:32:38,410
The surrender negotiation failed,
and now they’ve detained him.

563
00:32:38,410 --> 00:32:39,690
He’s in danger.

564
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:43,930
Song Chen, listen to me.

565
00:32:44,210 --> 00:32:45,820
You can't just stand here.

566
00:32:46,210 --> 00:32:48,380
Shanghai has already changed flags
and been liberated.

567
00:32:48,380 --> 00:32:49,930
This is the last reactionary stronghold.

568
00:32:49,930 --> 00:32:50,620
Take it down.

569
00:32:50,620 --> 00:32:51,620
You must take it.

570
00:32:51,620 --> 00:32:52,820
We don't have enough firepower.

571
00:32:52,820 --> 00:32:53,820
We're also short on manpower, Father.

572
00:32:53,820 --> 00:32:54,990
I've brought the ammunition.

573
00:32:54,990 --> 00:32:55,900
I'll go get it.

574
00:32:56,170 --> 00:32:57,830
Hurry, go get the ammunition!

575
00:32:59,100 --> 00:33:00,860
Li Xiehe has already ordered
the Zhabei Police

576
00:33:00,860 --> 00:33:01,860
to take fast boats

577
00:33:01,860 --> 00:33:03,950
and bypass the Settlement
to come as reinforcements.

578
00:33:03,950 --> 00:33:05,100
The Shanghai naval forces

579
00:33:05,100 --> 00:33:06,210
will also take sampans

580
00:33:06,210 --> 00:33:08,540
fully loaded with sailors to arrive here.

581
00:33:08,750 --> 00:33:09,550
That's great!

582
00:33:09,580 --> 00:33:11,280
You are my son.

583
00:33:11,410 --> 00:33:12,580
What’s happening today

584
00:33:12,580 --> 00:33:13,550
is what

585
00:33:13,580 --> 00:33:14,580
Napoleon called

586
00:33:14,580 --> 00:33:16,240
"the final fifteen minutes".

587
00:33:16,450 --> 00:33:17,650
Victory or defeat

588
00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:20,060
lies between your courage and timidity.

589
00:33:20,100 --> 00:33:21,930
If you don’t dare to take Ying Shi’s place

590
00:33:21,930 --> 00:33:23,330
and lead the death squad,

591
00:33:23,690 --> 00:33:24,410
then

592
00:33:25,010 --> 00:33:26,100
I will

593
00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:27,860
lead it myself.

594
00:33:27,860 --> 00:33:28,490
Father!

595
00:33:30,380 --> 00:33:32,040
You and Shuhong get in the car.

596
00:33:32,210 --> 00:33:33,210
Your son is now

597
00:33:33,210 --> 00:33:34,940
the Captain of the death squad.

598
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:45,390
Sacrifice for the revolution,
restore China!

599
00:33:45,930 --> 00:33:47,860
I am prepared to die tonight.

600
00:33:48,170 --> 00:33:49,690
Are you willing to go with me?

601
00:33:49,690 --> 00:33:51,580
At your command, Captain.

602
00:34:01,170 --> 00:34:01,770
You go

603
00:34:02,100 --> 00:34:03,100
take a few men upstairs

604
00:34:03,100 --> 00:34:03,930
and take out the machine gunners.

605
00:34:03,930 --> 00:34:05,170
Everyone else, hold your position.

606
00:34:05,170 --> 00:34:05,930
Yes.

607
00:35:08,930 --> 00:35:09,530
Charge!

608
00:35:09,610 --> 00:35:12,650
Charge!

609
00:37:21,380 --> 00:37:27,090
Charge!

610
00:37:27,700 --> 00:37:33,820
Charge!

611
00:37:37,710 --> 00:37:39,380
He has made it.

612
00:37:46,270 --> 00:37:50,020
[November 4, 1911.
September 14th,

613
00:37:50,020 --> 00:37:53,770
the 3rd year of Xuantong,
Shanghai is restored]

614
00:38:02,210 --> 00:38:05,050
[Luanzhou, Zhili]

615
00:38:06,880 --> 00:38:10,300
[Camp of the 20th Division]

616
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:08,470
Look at you.

617
00:38:09,570 --> 00:38:10,900
It's not over yet, is it?

618
00:38:10,970 --> 00:38:12,050
You little monkey!

619
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:15,580
You treacherous rebels!
What are you trying to do?

620
00:38:15,940 --> 00:38:17,730
Want to follow the Hubei rebels
and start an uprising, huh?

621
00:38:17,730 --> 00:38:18,660
Shut your mouth!

622
00:38:18,930 --> 00:38:19,940
Qing lackey.

623
00:38:19,970 --> 00:38:21,100
What right do you have to speak to me?

624
00:38:21,100 --> 00:38:21,930
Who are you calling a lackey?

625
00:38:21,930 --> 00:38:22,890
Who's the lackey?

626
00:38:22,890 --> 00:38:25,010
Xiao Yusong, everything you eat,
wear, and use

627
00:38:25,010 --> 00:38:26,320
was all bestowed by the Emperor.

628
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:26,840
And now

629
00:38:26,870 --> 00:38:28,310
I’m the lackey?

630
00:38:28,330 --> 00:38:29,110
And you’re the hero?

631
00:38:29,110 --> 00:38:29,710
Screw you!

632
00:38:29,740 --> 00:38:30,700
Slap him! Let's see if he's still a hero.

633
00:38:30,700 --> 00:38:31,650
Try it.

634
00:38:31,780 --> 00:38:33,530
Call me that again and I’ll slap you.

635
00:38:33,530 --> 00:38:35,300
You think that look is gonna scare me?

636
00:38:35,300 --> 00:38:36,340
Don't be shameless.

637
00:38:36,340 --> 00:38:37,050
Do you want me to slap you?

638
00:38:37,050 --> 00:38:39,110
Try slapping me and see what happens.

639
00:38:41,470 --> 00:38:42,590
You dare to hit me?

640
00:39:05,280 --> 00:39:06,320
What's going on?

641
00:39:07,490 --> 00:39:09,130
Fighting among ourselves?

642
00:39:09,970 --> 00:39:11,220
What a disgrace!

643
00:39:10,080 --> 00:39:11,960
[Zhang Shaozeng,
Commander of the 20th Division]

644
00:39:11,490 --> 00:39:13,600
He called me a Qing lackey.

645
00:39:13,750 --> 00:39:15,950
He called me a treacherous rebel!

646
00:39:16,300 --> 00:39:17,900
You are a treacherous rebel.

647
00:39:18,050 --> 00:39:18,930
That’s enough!

648
00:39:22,260 --> 00:39:24,970
Commander Yang has come
to our division for pacification.

649
00:39:24,970 --> 00:39:26,300
If you have anything to say,

650
00:39:26,300 --> 00:39:27,560
you can tell him later.

651
00:39:28,660 --> 00:39:29,520
Commander Yang

652
00:39:29,900 --> 00:39:32,030
also has something to say to everyone.

653
00:39:46,410 --> 00:39:47,380
Attention!

654
00:39:49,570 --> 00:39:50,570
Your Excellency.

655
00:39:50,640 --> 00:39:52,430
All officers at and above Colonel rank
in the 20th Division

656
00:39:52,430 --> 00:39:53,500
are all present.

657
00:39:53,530 --> 00:39:55,130
Please give us your instructions.

658
00:39:55,130 --> 00:39:56,010
Sit down.

659
00:39:59,450 --> 00:40:01,180
Officers of the 20th Division.

660
00:40:01,570 --> 00:40:02,300
Today,

661
00:40:02,490 --> 00:40:03,780
I

662
00:40:04,740 --> 00:40:05,570
want to use

663
00:40:05,570 --> 00:40:07,770
the prestige of Commander Yang Kaizhi,

664
00:40:07,970 --> 00:40:09,860
the recipient of
the Imperial Badge of the Double Dragon,

665
00:40:09,860 --> 00:40:11,780
the famous border defense hero,

666
00:40:12,090 --> 00:40:13,900
to strengthen the unity

667
00:40:13,930 --> 00:40:15,860
among our 20th division officers,

668
00:40:16,410 --> 00:40:17,970
and strive together for our great cause.

669
00:40:17,970 --> 00:40:19,370
We must not fail our duty.

670
00:40:24,050 --> 00:40:26,050
Youmin, what are you doing?

671
00:40:27,260 --> 00:40:28,970
This is a bomb with a fuse.

672
00:40:29,490 --> 00:40:30,570
Nobody moves!

673
00:40:30,860 --> 00:40:32,520
Move again and I'll hammer it.

674
00:40:33,020 --> 00:40:33,780
Sit down!

675
00:40:40,490 --> 00:40:42,050
Today, if anyone says

676
00:40:42,080 --> 00:40:43,810
anything against the Emperor,

677
00:40:44,300 --> 00:40:46,530
I'll hammer it.

678
00:40:46,930 --> 00:40:48,780
No one’s leaving this room!

679
00:40:48,970 --> 00:40:50,010
Don’t be reckless.

680
00:40:50,010 --> 00:40:50,570
Youmin.

681
00:40:50,820 --> 00:40:52,780
Commander Yang
is the Court’s special envoy.

682
00:40:52,780 --> 00:40:54,220
Here to pacify our division.

683
00:40:54,220 --> 00:40:55,780
Stop fooling around.

684
00:40:57,300 --> 00:40:58,560
Commander-in-chief.

685
00:41:00,220 --> 00:41:01,860
Court envoy?

686
00:41:02,870 --> 00:41:04,940
Everyone knows that Yang Kaizhi

687
00:41:04,970 --> 00:41:06,130
is a well-known

688
00:41:06,130 --> 00:41:08,130
veteran from Revolutionary Party.

689
00:41:21,150 --> 00:41:23,150
Am I right,

690
00:41:24,050 --> 00:41:25,910
Mr. Pacification Commissioner?

691
00:41:28,060 --> 00:41:30,020
You better watch your words.

692
00:41:30,260 --> 00:41:32,570
I have a short temper.

693
00:41:52,220 --> 00:41:53,950
The revolution you mentioned,

694
00:41:57,300 --> 00:41:58,500
what does it refer to?

695
00:41:59,780 --> 00:42:01,450
Why are you asking me?

696
00:42:01,970 --> 00:42:03,380
I'm asking you all.

697
00:42:03,780 --> 00:42:05,050
Your so-called revolution.

698
00:42:05,050 --> 00:42:06,390
What’s it really about?

699
00:42:08,740 --> 00:42:09,780
So,

700
00:42:10,560 --> 00:42:11,550
you're coercing me

701
00:42:11,550 --> 00:42:13,280
into answering your question.

702
00:42:14,340 --> 00:42:15,670
Call it that if you want.

703
00:42:16,110 --> 00:42:16,670
Alright.

704
00:42:17,340 --> 00:42:18,340
I'll answer you.

705
00:42:20,010 --> 00:42:21,970
The revolution that I believe in

706
00:42:22,460 --> 00:42:23,160
is nothing more than

707
00:42:23,160 --> 00:42:24,480
solving two issues.

708
00:42:25,130 --> 00:42:26,010
Which two?

709
00:42:26,380 --> 00:42:27,300
First,

710
00:42:28,080 --> 00:42:29,480
anyone who is not Chinese

711
00:42:29,780 --> 00:42:31,980
has no right to manage Chinese affairs.

712
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:34,230
This is the spirit of nationalism.

713
00:42:34,820 --> 00:42:35,740
And the second?

714
00:42:36,040 --> 00:42:37,330
Every Chinese

715
00:42:37,750 --> 00:42:40,010
has the right to manage Chinese affairs.

716
00:42:40,110 --> 00:42:41,910
This is the spirit of democracy.

717
00:42:43,930 --> 00:42:44,740
I don't see

718
00:42:44,740 --> 00:42:46,340
what this has to do with me

719
00:42:46,860 --> 00:42:48,530
or with

720
00:42:48,560 --> 00:42:50,000
any of us here.

721
00:42:53,780 --> 00:42:55,300
Who pays my wages?

722
00:42:55,540 --> 00:42:57,020
Who offers me a job?

723
00:42:57,970 --> 00:42:59,600
All just fancy talk

724
00:42:59,720 --> 00:43:01,870
made up by you scholars.
